TEXT.S: = Laidazuan(malavi) = Gaga mniq Nantowseyn Sinyisyang ka alang Laidazuan(malavi). 227 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 782 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 97% niqan 757 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 3% niqan 25 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Bunun94%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq1%, Amis1%, ni rahuq na o1%.
